"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-29-olympic-skateboarders-young-21318443\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Why are skateboarders at theOlympicsso young?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 45, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can certainly be forgiven for asking that question.\", \"from\": 46, \"to\": 101, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB's very ownSky Brownhad only just turned 13 when she won bronze at theTokyo Olympics in 2021and became Britain's youngest ever medallist.\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 247, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even now - as sherepresents the nationinParis- she's still only 16 years old, as is teammate Lola Tambling.\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 356, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 342, \"end\": 346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lola_Cars\", \"score\": 0.9999999999749889, \"rank\": 2.132458036525704e-11, \"text\": \"Lola\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lola_Cars\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lola_Cars\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The gold medal in the women's street finals at the start of the games was won by 14-year-old Coco Yoshizawa fromJapan.\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 476, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics  Silver and bronze were picked up by 15-year-old Liz Akama from Japan and Brazil's Rayssa Leal, 16, respectively, in a final where the average age of the eight competitors was just 15.8 years.\", \"from\": 478, \"to\": 742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 536, \"end\": 549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 614, \"end\": 619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9997574616945912, \"rank\": 0.00023690485754587824, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 624, \"end\": 630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5875845155689308, \"rank\": 0.6990757563963877, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 633, \"end\": 644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rayssa_Leal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rayssa Leal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rayssa_Leal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rayssa_Leal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are of course older skaters, including Britain's Andy Macdonald, who will be 51 by the time he takes to the park andbecomes the country's oldest Olympian.\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 904, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 789, \"end\": 796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9990390564724485, \"rank\": 0.0009612695435533528, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 799, \"end\": 813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\", \"score\": 0.9999978194979248, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andy Macdonald\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\"}, {\"begin\": 895, \"end\": 903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999981346264, \"rank\": 1.8651973325492735e-09, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But a vast majority of skateboarding athletes are teenagers, which can not help but leave you wondering why that's the case.\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 1030, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'There is no science behind why youngsters achieve such success in the sport,' says Team GB on its official page.\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1145, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1116, \"end\": 1123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9987488444670224, \"rank\": 0.0012527227364884175, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Although it's important to note that the likes of Team GB's Andy Macdonald will turn 51 during Paris 2024.'\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1255, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1198, \"end\": 1205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9987488444670224, \"rank\": 0.0012527227364884175, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1208, \"end\": 1222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\", \"score\": 0.9999978194979248, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andy Macdonald\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB says: 'The sport attracts young children and teens through its comradery in the skatepark and the enticement of getting a trick just right.\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1257, \"end\": 1264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9987488444670224, \"rank\": 0.0012527227364884175, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Add that to the fearless nature of Olympic skateboarders, teenagers seem to be dominating the sporting stage.'\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And it's that comradery and fearlessness that BBC commentator Ed Leigh believes contributes to why skateboarders are so young - as well as the fact their bodies are able to tolerate the brutal impact the sport has on them.\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1581, \"end\": 1589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ed_Leigh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ed Leigh\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ed_Leigh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ed_Leigh\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's terrifyingly physical and you have to understand how much commitment it takes,' he told the i newspaper at Tokyo 2020.\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1867, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1856, \"end\": 1861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999998668195165, \"rank\": 1.325681809563395e-07, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Anyone who has stepped on a skateboard has fallen off, and there is a good saying, it does not matter how rich you are, you can not buy a trick, you have to pay with pain.\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 2041, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'That's the only way around it.\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2074, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's something shared between all skateboarders.\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2125, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A camaraderie.\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You know to get that good you have overcome some big slams and stayed committed to it.\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Action sports are based in skill acquisition.\", \"from\": 2229, \"to\": 2275, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The younger you are, the bendier and softer you are when you try and get those skills, the quicker you can recover.\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2391, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'You have athletes by 21, 22, talking about recovery time, the fact is they can not just keep skating.'\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2496, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB star Macdonald believes age is nothing but a number, however - and is proving it by the mere fact he's in contention in the men's park event on August 7.\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2659, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: 'Everyone asks about my age, it's generally the mainstream media that is like \\\"woah, you are this crazy 51-year-old at the skate park\\\".\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2805, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'But I have been here, it's not like I just showed up.\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2861, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was already at the skate park when these kids showed up.\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 2920, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'In what other sport do you see, at a competitive level, teenagers and 50-year-olds competing together?\", \"from\": 2922, \"to\": 3025, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We all share this bond.\", \"from\": 3026, \"to\": 3049, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Skateboarding is literally my fountain of youth.'\", \"from\": 3051, \"to\": 3101, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 3103, \"to\": 3151, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 3153, \"to\": 3223, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Olympian sent home for compla